Shareholders' Meeting
The Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders of Daiwa Securities Group Inc. is held annually in late June.
						Shareholders who own 1,000 shares or more and are listed on the shareholders' list at the end of March are entitled to exercise voting rights at the Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders.
The 80th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders was held on Wednesday, June 28, 2017 at The Prince Park Tower Tokyo in Tokyo.

The 80th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders

 Notice of Convocation of the 80th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders (  1,064KB)
 Disclosed Information on the Internet in relation to the Notice of Convocation (  255KB)
(FYI) Notice of Convocation of the 80th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders (including Disclosed Information on the Internet) (  1,312KB)
					* Above two files are combined into one file for your convenience.
The notice of convocation of the 80th ordinary general meeting of shareholders was sent via postal mail on June 2, 2017. We disclosed the notice on the internet before mailing to provide the information to shareholders as swift as possible.

 Notice of Results of Exercise of Voting Rights at the 80th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders(  120KB)


