About Us
Daiwa Capital Markets America Inc. was formed in 1964 as a wholly owned subsidiary of Daiwa Securities Co. Ltd. It started its business focusing mainly on the sales of Japanese equities to U.S. institutional investors.




Services
We offer a comprehensive range of financial products and services.


Disclosure documents
It is our goal to provide service beyond expectations through a strong network.






SEC Rule 605 and 606

Daiwa Securities Group Inc.



